
MIP 2
"multum in parvo"
(much in little)

plugin wrappers, abstractions, simplifications, helpers, ..

v0.0.0
in progress, prototype, proof of concept, pre-, ..


* os: linux (windows considered)
* plugin: clap, exe, vst2, vst3, (maybe lv2)
* host: clap (other formats coming, ladspa/dssi dropped)
* gui: xcb (cairo coming)
* io: jack audio/midi
* other: too much to list..


* headers-only
* un-modern, un-cool c++
* (semi-) modular
* no (minimal) dependencies
* permissive license
* ...


* make it work
* make it right
* make it fast, small, stable, bugfree, pretty, etc..


----------


https://raw.githubusercontent.com/skei/MIP2/master/screenshots/gui_old.png
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8gMQY8lFopg


----------


g++ -Wall -std=c++14 -fPIC -g -rdynamic -Wl,-Bsymbolic -DMIP_DEBUG -I../src -c build.cpp -o build.o
g++ -shared build.o -o mip_debug.so -fPIE -lpthread -ldl -lxcb -lxcb-util -lxcb-image -lxcb-cursor -lxcb-keysyms -lcairo -lsndfile


